descriptionHtml:
This is one of the various presets I have used in my playthroughs and the first one I gave uploaded to Nexus.

[b][i][font=Tahoma]Requirements
[/font][/i][/b]SKSE (obviously)
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/29624/?]RaceMenu[/url] by Expired
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/30411/?]Brows[/url] by Hvergelmir
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/31665/?]Better Makeup for SKSE[/url] by Diethardt
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/68311/?]KS Hairdos - Renewal[/url] by Kalilies Stealthic Khaos and Shocky
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/13722/?]The Eyes of Beauty[/url] by Gabriel Mailhot as LogRaam
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/35327/?]SG Female Eyebrows[/url] by Hello Santa
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/35677/?]The Coenaculi[/url] by Desufire

To make it look like it does in the screenshots
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/36067/?]Vividian ENB[/url] by Mangaclub and Benhat
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/51602/?]Fair Skin Complexion[/url] by HHaleyy

[font=Tahoma][b][i]Installation[/i][/b][/font]
1.Copy files into Data directory. Replace if necessary.
OR
  Use NMM.

2.Open racemenu using console command [b]showracemenu.
[/b]
3.In the presets tab, load the Cassandra.jslot .

4.In the sculpt tab, import head Cassandra.NIF .

5.That's it. The preset has been tested on all human races as well as high and wood elves.
   For dark elves there is a ridge on the forehead

[b][size=3]            ENJOY!!![/size][/b]
author: sab3r2th
